This paper proposes a new method for instance segmentation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces improvements to the backbone network, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed method involves object detection, which is related to robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the paper presents results on a benchmark dataset, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
